335
00:33:13,951 --> 00:33:18,237
[SPEAKER_05]: Investment has gone in, and we've also increased the numbers of teachers that we have.

336
00:33:18,217 --> 00:33:20,401
[SPEAKER_05]: 30,000 more teachers.

337
00:33:20,761 --> 00:33:26,411
[SPEAKER_05]: That is absolutely vital and education standards are going up as a direct consequence of that.

338
00:33:26,511 --> 00:33:29,436
