342
00:33:48,327 --> 00:33:48,608
[SPEAKER_03]: Life-changing.

343
00:33:48,628 --> 00:33:50,190
[SPEAKER_03]: But you're supposed to have fallen down the international rankings.

344
00:33:50,210 --> 00:33:51,452
[SPEAKER_11]: Absolutely life-changing.

345
00:33:51,853 --> 00:33:54,838
[SPEAKER_11]: And I don't know if the Lib Dems agree with tuition fees or not.

346
00:33:54,858 --> 00:33:57,242
[SPEAKER_11]: They've got quite a record in that regard.

347
00:33:57,262 --> 00:33:59,445
[SPEAKER_11]: I'm sure you can elaborate upon it for all of us.

