362
00:34:43,467 --> 00:34:45,913
[SPEAKER_13]: Our education system is being run into the ground.

363
00:34:46,374 --> 00:34:52,367
[SPEAKER_13]: And I was really glad to see the National Education Union came out yesterday to welcome the Green Party manifesto.

364
00:34:52,768 --> 00:34:56,837
[SPEAKER_13]: It said that the Green Party manifesto is the only party manifesto out so far.

365
00:34:56,817 --> 00:35:00,064
